This is some code to run GLTPS models a la Wang and Ranalli (2007)

You probably want to install the msg package (from github.com/dill/msg), soap (from www.maths.bath.ac.uk/~sw283/simon/software.html) and mgcv (from CRAN) to get it to work.

YMMV.


References:

Wang, H. and Ranalli, M.G. (2007). Low-rank smoothing splines on complicated domains. Biometrics 63(1), 209--217



